Mr Price Advances Most in More Than a Week as Its Annual Profit Climbs 45%

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-05-26T07:09:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/mr-price-advances-most-in-more-than-a-week-as-its-annual-profit-climbs-45-.html
Mr Price Group Ltd. (MPC) , a South African
clothing and furniture retailer, rose to the highest in more
than a week after saying operating profit advanced 45 percent in
the year through April.  The stock rallied as much as 4.3 percent to 66 rand and
traded 2.1 percent higher at 64.60 rand by 9:07 a.m. in
Johannesburg, the strongest intraday level since May 17.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  